{"tid":2364469,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家都話工作離唔開whatsapp 點解唔試下寄信比大機構叫佢地帶頭用signal?","createTime":"2021-01-13T04:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T09:54:41.000Z","uid":110080,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c667e0e121bc2fd4d4456ed1f849acfd08e80cf","tid":2364469,"uid":110080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:26:14.000Z","msg":"呢幾日轉唔轉signal 都產生左好多爭議<br />\n<br />\n其中一樣好大既爭議就係工作上擺脫唔到 (先唔講其他爭議先）<br />\n<br />\n既然如此，我地可以試下寄信or send email 比各大機構（公營機構，大學，銀行，上市大公司 etc)<br />\n<br />\n指出基於私隱問題要求佢地使用signal <br />\n當然 要叫佢地即時放棄whatsapp 係無可能<br />\n但如果只係要求佢地提供多一個signal 渠道去比人contact <br />\n我相信成件事會可行好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要有大公司踏出第一步就一切都會順理成章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時大家就可以係公司內光明正大咁叫人公事都用signal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ceadb493d44f0f6295ba3b137a071c49ee5cce","tid":2364469,"uid":210161,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:35:15.000Z","msg":"叫老細叫客改用sinal去遷就你班junior<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077be7407136728fa5fb36dd236309e0476a5ea6","tid":2364469,"uid":110080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a7ceadb493d44f0f6295ba3b137a071c49ee5cce","tid":2364469,"uid":210161,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:35:15.000Z","msg":"叫老細叫客改用sinal去遷就你班junior<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"唔係叫佢改用signal 放棄WhatsApp <br />\n只係叫佢提供多個渠道比客聯絡"},{"pid":"f4e91582f881cd88a3a437643e1d2afaba388a84","tid":2364469,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif